{"id":25376564231,"name":"Run api tests","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAF6I-kBw","head_branch":"DHIS2-fr-trim-deletion-hotfix","head_sha":"b044beb3933654f378439c9a78c5ab79c1d81740","path":".github/workflows/run-api-tests.yml","run_number":49492,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"fix: emergency disable file resource cleanup until trim SQL is fixed [DHIS2-21427]","status":"completed","conclusion":"success","workflow_id":5591308,"check_suite_id":67529390144,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAAPuRC4QA","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/25376564231","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/25376564231","created_at":"2026-05-05T12:32:57Z","updated_at":"2026-05-05T12:46:24Z","run_started_at":"2026-05-05T12:32:57Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/25376564231/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/25376564231/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/67529390144","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/25376564231/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/25376564231/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/25376564231/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"fix: emergency disable file resource cleanup until trim SQL is fixed [DHIS2-21427]\n\nThe DATA_VALUE_TRIM job's SQL in HibernateDataValueTrimStore only scans\nthe aggregate datavalue table, so file resources referenced from\ntrackerevent.eventdatavalues JSONB and trackedentityattributevalue.value\nare wrongly flipped to isassigned=false. The FileResourceCleanUpJob then\ndeletes those FRs and their underlying files on the next run, unless\nkeyFileResourceRetentionStrategy=FOREVER. Customers have reported file\nloss starting March 2026 (after upgrading to 2.41.7+ / 2.42.4 / 2.43-pre).\n\nThis is an emergency patch that disables both the deletion path and the\nbuggy flip:\n\n  - FileResourceCleanUpJob.execute() — DV-domain cleanup block removed\n  - HibernateDataValueTrimStore.updateFileResources*ToAnyDataValue() —\n    both methods return 0 (no-op)\n  - FileResourceCleanUpJobTest — fr15 assertion flipped to assertNotNull\n    to reflect the new behavior\n\nKnown regressions while this patch is in effect:\n\n  - Cleanup of legitimately-orphaned DV-domain FRs is paused. Disk usage\n    grows slowly until the proper SQL fix lands.\n  - Wrongly-unassigned FRs from prior runs are not repaired by this patch.\n    They will be auto-repaired on the next nightly DATA_VALUE_TRIM run\n    after the proper SQL fix is deployed (via the symmetric\n    updateFileResourcesAssignedToAnyDataValue once it learns about events\n    and TEAVs).\n\nFollowups:\n\n  - Proper SQL fix (widen both update* methods to UNION-ALL aggregate +\n    trackerevent JSONB + singleevent JSONB + TEAVs) ships separately.\n  - Backports for 2.41 / 2.42 / 2.43 will be applied once this lands.\n\nAI Assisted\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"netroms@gmail.com"},"id":"b044beb3933654f378439c9a78c5ab79c1d81740","tree_id":"02bdb5f6897b92261ff6d0574a742054f3673ec9","timestamp":"2026-05-05T12:27:45Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"netroms@gmail.com"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_u